nodes.text: The Kaitis Cartel was a fictitious criminal organization created by Sith Lord Darth Maul. Maul posed as one of the cartel's enforcers and worked with the thief Zek Peiro in intercepting scarn shipments. The organization was named after the Rutian Twi'lek Padawan Eldra Kaitis, the first Jedi that Maul had killed.
